接口 CompilationUnitTree

  • 所有超级接口:

    所有已知实现类:

    @Exported
public interface CompilationUnitTree
extends Tree
    Represents the abstract syntax tree for compilation units (source files) and package declarations (package-info.java).
    从以下版本开始:
    1.6
    作者:
    Peter von der Ahé
